OL,6,FPrime minister Sir Keir Starmer is
OL,7,Furging councils to prove they are
OL,8,Ftackling potholes or face losing the
OL,9,Fcash to fix them.
OL,11,FThe PM said councils need to "get on
OL,12,Fwith the job" of fixing potholes as he
OL,13,Fannounced an additional #4.8 billion
OL,14,Fof funding to carry out work on
OL,15,Fmotorways and major A-roads.
